image.altText: Lines of solar panels on a paddock

image.altText: Donald Trump scowls at the camera sitting in court in a suit.

image.altText: A man in a black baseball cap and black T-shirt sits in front of a window.

image.altText: A profile image of a white woman with dark brown hair.
